event.description:
Join us for this rare live performance by Award-winning singer-songwriter, Jenny Bruce, at Rockwood&#39;s Stage 3!  Jenny will perform her original songs from her latest album, Firefly in a Jar, out now on iTunes and all other digital sites. Paste Magazine raves, &quot;&quot;she weaves [stories] into the fabric of her songs that unfolds for her listeners so effortlessly, like a soft linen handkerchief in the warm summer breeze...I was blown away.&quot;&quot;

Firefly in Jar is Jenny&#39;s fourth album out over her successful 15 year career. She has shared the stages with the likes of Avril Lavigne, Gavin DeGraw, Joe Jackson, and Toby Lightman. Jenny has also won several songwriting awards, including the Billboard Song Contest, the Great American Songwriting Contest, and the John Lennon Songwriting Contest. In addition, her songs have been heard on multiply national TV shows, including All My Children (ABC), Ghost Whisperer (CBS), The Today Show (NBC), Dawson&#39;s Creek (WB) and King of the Hill (FOX).

Be sure to &quot;catch&quot; Jenny Bruce at Rockwood on October 20th!
